Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.69,0:00:09.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.74,0:00:19.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:39.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:06.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.97,0:01:14.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:20.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:27.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:20.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,You just said,\N"This will be easy," didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:28.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,That fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:32.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simile Simoun\Nis a Simoun prototype...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:36.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,It hasn't received\Nthe grace of Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:39.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,It can't draw a Ri Majon wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:47.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Blue Spring
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:56.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Such beautiful lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:59.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Watch closely. M? U isn't just practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:04.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because it'll be your souls and\Nbodies that control the Simouns' flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:08.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Elly, why are\Nyou dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:16.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the last time I'll ever\Nsee anything as beautiful as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:24.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the emerald pattern...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:34.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's she thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:44.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Does this look like a real Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:58.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:03:59.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,She enlisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:03.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Enlisted? That's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:09.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who'd volunteer at a time like this,\Nknowing they'd have to go into battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:28.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:59.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you in Tempest too?\NNobody else joined the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:01.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:02.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:04.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I was alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:07.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simulating the Emerald\NRi Majon of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:10.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,How would that make\NNeviril feel if she saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:13.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was I doing a Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:17.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who's Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:21.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,When Simoun sibyllae take to the\Nskies, it's called praying to the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:25.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Make sure you never\Nuse the word battle again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:33.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,So who's Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril is the regina of Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:41.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea, the Golden Priestess!\NI want to pair up with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:42.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:46.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why not?\NShe's the top Simoun rider, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:52.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it might not be true anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:58.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're amazing!\NI think I really like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:00.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't you pair up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:03.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, where's this Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:40.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,It brings back memories.\NWhen we were trainees...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:44.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,...nothing made me happier\Nthan waiting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,That hasn't changed one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:50.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dressed like that...\Nyou're leaving the ship too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:55.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. Since it's been a long\Ntime since my 17th birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:59.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've decided to go to the Spring.\NAnd I have one last favor to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:01.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:09.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,...of going to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:12.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:20.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course, Elly.\NI will accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:24.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril! Anyone seen Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:30.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop calling her that. Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,...um, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:36.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is Chor Tempest's\Nmaintenance hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:38.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where's Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:41.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,You here, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:44.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the cafeteria.\NAnd this is the ballroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where's Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the forward deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:01.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:03.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Elly said she's going to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:07.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's unpaired at the moment,\Nso I'm accompanying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:11.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're lying.\NThen why are you taking luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:15.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I haven't made up my mind yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:21.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,So there's a chance that\NI might enter the Spring as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:23.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:25.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,But you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:28.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can't do that!\NBecause if you enter the Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:33.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that means you'll have Tempus\NSpatium choose your gender, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:34.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:36.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:41.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer. Chor Tempest Simoun sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:44.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd like to pair up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:48.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those who are neither male\Nnor female can fly Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now's our only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:54.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yet if you go to the Spring,\Nyou can't be my pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:57.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,She couldn't to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:09:02.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,My 17th birthday\Npassed over a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:05.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're an exceptional Simoun sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:10.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and in this state of emergency,\Nthe nation can't afford to lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:14.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,So Onasia has agreed not\Nto summon you to the Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:16.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:23.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:32.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are all born as females.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:38.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,But to create a society,\Nhalf the population must be male.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:43.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tempus Spatium has decreed\Nthe world should be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:48.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Once we've turned 17, we're allowed\Nto choose our permanent gender.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:54.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,But in the case of Simoun sibyllae,\Nthis can be delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:59.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our nation, Kyuukoku, has gotten\Ninvaded by countless countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our only hope of battling\Nthem are Simouns...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:07.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and you sibyllae,\Nwho can talk with the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:12.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you wish, you may delay\Nyour pilgrimage to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:17.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,If, on the other hand, you yearn for\Nthe Spring, we cannot stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:20.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Especially Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:26.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since the war began, you and Chor\NCaput have suffered great losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:31.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those who've turned 17 are free\Nto choose the same path as Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:33.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no way I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:38.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Man or woman, I haven't\Ndecided yet. I don't even want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:42.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm in battle with a Simoun,\NI won't have to go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:46.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I came here.\NAre you guys different?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:50.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,No question.\NOnce you're of age, you have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:54.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,It means you're going\Nto become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:58.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,But right now, the nation\Nneeds our powers, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:00.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:05.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then you've all already decided\Nto become a man or woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:09.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you, Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:33.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's fine, Elly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:37.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,One last time...\NWon't you pair up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:41.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want you to see me fly as\Nan auriga to the great temple below.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:47.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then I'll have them\Nget a Simoun ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:57.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well? How's my driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:00.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not "driving,"\N"speaking with the Simoun."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:02.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I'm just so psyched.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:06.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because this is the first time\NI've touched a real Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:08.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,First time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:13.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to ride one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:17.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:19.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everything has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:24.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're not "praying to\Nthe skies" for Tempus Spatium...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:26.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but for war?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:27.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:29.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:32.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:37.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,What kind...\NWhat kind of place the battlefield is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:45.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do. Because I trained\Non the front lines in the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:52.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Before the war, sibyllae would go to\Nthe Spring when they turned 17, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:53.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:59.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,But now, the great temple's laws\Nsay we don't have to go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:02.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,As long as we're winning this war...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:22.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,How rude. She's an auriga, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:28.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,So she made you fly as her sagitta?\NThe finest auriga in the nation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:45.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Out of all of us here, is Paraietta\Nthe only one who's turned 17?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:49.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister, you'll be\N17 next month, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:57.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Either way, we all will be soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:02.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going after Neviril?\NYou're going to become a man for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,You made\Nthat decision long ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:10.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I still feel that there are things\NI need to accomplish here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:50.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Elly, have you decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:54.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which gender you'll\Nchoose at the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:00.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:02.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:07.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've always been female, so I think\Nit'd be more natural to stay one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:10.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I might also want to become a male.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:15.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all, there aren't a lot of job\Nopportunities unless you're a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:23.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know you must be weary,\NSimoun sibylla, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:26.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:33.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun sibylla...\NSuch a beautiful sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:37.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,O priestess, please guide\Nour nation to the righteous path.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:55.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:04.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I'm with you,\NI think I'll have fun flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:49.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,O sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:54.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are overjoyed to know that\Nyour time for prayer is now over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:17:00.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,We thank you for having\Nprotected us all thus far...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:40.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:43.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to think\N"male" or "female" in my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:47.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what happens if I think of both?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:51.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.\NThere's nothing to worry about, Elly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:55.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:03.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Great Priestess Onasia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:10.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for not journeying here\Nthough my 17th birthday is long past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:15.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Elly, enter the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:17.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,And offer a prayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:01.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:04.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should I do? I can't decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:28.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,The holy sounds of Tempus Spatium\Nhave just been bestowed upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:47.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was told that starting\Ntoday, my name is Eliph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:49.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:52.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:55.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,They say your voice\Nchanges overtime...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:59.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and your chest gets smaller, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:04.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing's really changed, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:06.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:10.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing has changed, Eliph.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:46.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, Sibylla Roatreamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:48.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're staying too, my lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:53.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,I grew up being told\NI should become a sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:55.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,...so if I went home now,\Nthey'd yell at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:21:00.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,We all have one, don't we? A reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:18.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,The thing is...\NI can't fly this alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:52.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,You didn't go to the Spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:56.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,I did go. But I decided not to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:08.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Than our ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.42,0:22:12.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:14.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.12,0:22:47.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:52.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.07,0:22:59.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:06.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:19.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:24.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.76,0:23:28.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.81,0:23:32.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:38.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.71,0:23:44.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.23,0:23:47.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:53.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.33,0:23:59.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:06.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:11.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shoukoku's massive long-range cannons are\Nheaded this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.61,0:24:16.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.85,0:24:18.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Distant War.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.47,0:24:19.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Distant War
